description: Blueone Card Inc. provides payout solutions and prepaid cards to consumers in the United States and internationally. It operates as a reseller of an all-in-one branded card with various user benefits, such as no overdraft fees, no interest fees, virtual bank accounts, and free direct deposit. The company was formerly known as Manneking Inc. and changed its name to Blueone Card Inc. in July 2020. Blueone Card Inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Newport Beach, California.
